{"tid":299421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁愛詩：倘沒證據越境執法　批評言論屬多餘","createTime":"2017-06-27T05:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T06:43:20.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44db7f12906625a36b7936c58f0e0d9088f920cc","tid":299421,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會副主任梁愛詩表示，若無證據顯示有內地人員曾在港越境執法，她認為相關批評是「多餘」，市民應要尊重各司法管轄區的法治。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩出席一個網台節目後，被問到高鐵「一地兩檢」的安排時表示，基本法的框架下有空間進行清關工作，如果有意願就能做到，但現時特區政府仍未公布討論細節的結果，她不便評論，以免影響政府的商討過程。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩又說，政府商討後亦要將文件交往立法會，屆時可再討論是否接受，若無「一地兩檢」，代表乘客要在邊境下車接受清關檢查，高鐵便會失去優勢及作用。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1338505-20170627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1338505-20170627.htm&d=rXCVhASnXJoK16ypx%2F2IBMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c0f1eae8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1338505-20170627.htm&h=5d1f0e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1338505-20170627.htm</a><br />\n香港法律精神係未證實有罪前,被告是無辜的~"},{"pid":"619b1fdc02b08a984273bc4067d640b552ee7bb5","tid":299421,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:17:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93a619632c86e711f80a74da79f5ede9fdd06a1d","tid":299421,"uid":14144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:19:47.000Z","msg":"唔係無辜 係嫌疑啫"},{"pid":"6aef1c516642ca2614bca1484f3a7da70375ef2e","tid":299421,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇出境紀錄已經係證據</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李波：我偷渡番去比佢拉架<br />\n<br />\n李旺洋：我自殺架"},{"pid":"cea049cba20697d69b73f51bfcf7dfed51be4234","tid":299421,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇出境紀錄已經係證據</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁應該告李波非法出入境"}]}